This is a Remix + TypeScript project with Tailwind CSS.

STYLING RULES:
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for ALL styling
- Do NOT create CSS modules — use Tailwind classes inline in JSX
- Follow mobile-first responsive design (sm:, md:, lg: breakpoints)
- Tailwind CSS is imported in app/root.tsx

IMPORTANT:
- Always run `npm install && npm run dev` to start
- Use TypeScript for all new files (.tsx, .ts)
- Never use `remix dev` directly — always use `npm run dev`
